{"article_id":"fMQ5u36f5XTTzqBa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"- the Palo Alto University professor","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"who has accused Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh of sexual assault -","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"has agreed to testify about the allegations in front of the Senate Judiciary Committee on Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Ford ' s attorneys on Sunday confirmed","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that Ford will appear before the committee at 10 am on Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"\" Despite actual threats to her safety and her life ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Dr. Ford believes","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"it is important for Senators to hear directly from her about the sexual assault","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"committed against her , \"","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Ford ' s attorneys said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"They said","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"no decision has been made yet","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"about who will question Ford","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"- whether it will be lawmakers or staff attorneys .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The New York Times reported previously","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"that during a brief call on Saturday , aides to Iowa Republican Sen. Chuck Grassley , the chairman of the committee , and Ford ' s lawyers tentatively agreed to the date .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"\" Dr . Ford accepts the Committee ' s request","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"to provide her first-hand knowledge of Brett Kavanaugh ' s sexual misconduct next week , \"","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"wrote Debra Katz and Lisa Banks , two of Ford ' s attorneys , on Saturday prior to the date agreement .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"\" Although many aspects of the proposal","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"you provided via email , on September 21 , 2018 , at 2:33 pm ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"are fundamentally inconsistent with the Committee ' s promise of a fair , impartial investigation into her allegations ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"and we are disappointed with the leaks and the bullying","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"that have tainted the process ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"we are hopeful","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"that we can reach agreement on details . \"","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Republicans have said","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"that they are interested in hearing from Ford ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"but negotiations over what that will look like had grown increasingly contentious in the last few days .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"Grassley had given Ford until 2:30pm on Saturday to offer the committee a more definitive response about her testimony .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Democrats , meanwhile , have accused Republicans of bullying Ford","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"and continuing to rush the process .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Just agreeing on a hearing has required days of back-and-forth","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"After coming forward in a Washington Post article last weekend","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"in which she accused Kavanaugh of forcing himself on her","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"while they were at a party in high school ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Ford said","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"she wanted to cooperate with lawmakers","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"and is interested in having her story heard .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Kavanaugh has unequivocally denied the accusations .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"But several days of uncertainty","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"about whether she would appear before the committee","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"followed .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Grassley had previously issued three earlier deadlines","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"( Friday at 10am , 5 pm , and then 10 pm )","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"for a response from Ford ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"which","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Katz argued","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"were \" aggressive and artificial \"","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"and ran counter to claims","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that the panel wanted to genuinely consider Ford ' s perspective .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"\" You have been tasked with pressuring Dr. Ford to agree to conditions","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"that you find advantageous to the nominee , \"","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"Katz wrote .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"Grassley ultimately extended that deadline to Saturday afternoon .","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"Grassley didn ' t appear to be happy about the extension ,","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"despite granting it .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"In a tweet on Friday , he complained","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"that he feels like","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"he ' s \" playing 2nd trombone in the judiciary orchestra","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"and [ Senate Minority Leader Chuck ] Schumer is the conductor .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"\" With all the extensions","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"we give Dr Ford","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"to decide","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"if she still wants to testify to the Senate","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"I feel like","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"I ' m playing 2nd trombone in the judiciary orchestra","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"and Schumer is the conductor","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"- ChuckGrassley","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"( @ ChuckGrassley )","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"September 22 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Ford ' s attorney had said Thursday","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"that she was still negotiating the terms","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"under which she would testify in front of the Senate Judiciary Committee .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"She had said","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"that it was \" not possible \" for her to attend the public hearing","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"originally scheduled for Monday ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"but that she \" wishes to testify ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"provided that we can agree on terms","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"that are fair","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"and which ensure her safety , \"","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"according to an email","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"obtained by the Washington Post .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"An unnamed Republican senator told Politico","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"the committee has agreed to some of Ford ' s requests ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"which include ensuring that she and Kavanaugh are not in the same room .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"\" We ' ll do it on Wednesday ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"we expect the accuser before the accused","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"and we do intend to have the counsel do the questioning , \"","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"the senator said .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Republicans on the committee have indicated","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"that they were interested in moving ahead with a vote on Kavanaugh ' s nomination","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"if Ford didn ' t testify .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"Grassley appeared to follow through on this threat","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"by scheduling a committee vote on Kavanaugh for Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"which would have taken place","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"if Ford declined to appear .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"\" In the event","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that we can come to a reasonable resolution","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"as I ' ve been seeking all week ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"then I will postpone the committee vote","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"to accommodate her testimony .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"We can not continue to delay , \"","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"Grassley said in a Friday statement before the extension .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"One of the major sticking points was the committee ' s proposed structure for the hearing .","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"\" The Committee ' s stated plan","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"to move forward with a hearing","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"that has only two witnesses","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"is not a fair or good faith investigation ;","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"there are multiple witnesses","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"whose names have appeared publicly","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"and should be included in any proceeding , \"","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Banks wrote in a statement earlier this week .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"Ford and Kavanaugh are currently the only two witnesses","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"expected to testify .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Democrats have argued","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"that others ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"including Mark Judge ,","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"whom Ford implicated in the assault as part of her accusation ,","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"should speak as well .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Ford had said","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"that Judge helped Kavanaugh push her into a bedroom at the party","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"and was intermittently encouraging Kavanaugh during the alleged assault .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"Judge has said","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"he has no recollection of this incident","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"and that he never saw Kavanaugh act in this way .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Ford ' s attorneys on Sunday pointed out","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"that the committee has refused to subpoena Judge","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"or invite other witnesses to testify .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"The Times reported on Saturday","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"that a woman","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"named Leland Keyser ,","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"who was believed to have been at the party with Ford ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"told the committee","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"that she \" does not know \" Kavanaugh","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"and has \" no recollection \"","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"of being at a party or gathering","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"where he was present .","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"Judge and one other man","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"also said to have been at the party","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"also told the committee","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"they don ' t remember it ,","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"meaning Ford has no corroborating witnesses .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"Ford and her lawyers also threw up breaks over ( the lack of ) an FBI investigation :","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"Ford had said","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"she wouldn ' t testify","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"unless the FBI first conducted an investigation into the allegations ,","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"but it doesn ' t look like that ' s going to happen anytime soon .","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"Judiciary Republicans , the Department of Justice , and President Donald Trump have all thrown cold water on the idea of an FBI investigation .","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"Grassley on Wednesday said","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"it was not the job of the FBI to weigh the \" credibility \" of these allegations .","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"Ford ' s call for an FBI probe echoes one","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"that Democrats have been making","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"ever since she came forward .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"The review","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"they are pushing","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"wouldn ' t be a new criminal investigation","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"but a reopening of Kavanaugh ' s existing background check .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"The FBI may not be responsible","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"for determining how seriously to consider allegations ,","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"but the agency plays a pivotal role","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"in fact-finding and interviewing witnesses ,","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"they argue .","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"In the wake of Anita Hill ' s sexual harassment allegations against Clarence Thomas in 1991 , President George H.W . Bush directed the FBI to open an investigation .","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"The agency interviewed Hill , Thomas , and at least one other witness ,","depth":13},{"id":166,"text":"after which the White House determined","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"that Hill ' s allegations were \" unfounded . \"","depth":14},{"id":168,"text":"It ' s well within Trump ' s ability to do the same ,","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"but thus far , he ' s shown little inclination","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"that he ' s interested in doing so .","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"Ford ' s decision","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"to testify","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"suggests","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"she ' s accepted the outcome","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"and remains ready to speak out on her own","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"rather than let the process continue","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"without senators hearing what she has to say .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":355,"left":221,"right":354,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":204,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":192,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":188,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":181,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":180,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":180,"left":0,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":182,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":185,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":6,"right":184,"relation":"adversativ